  "description": "\nThe Sign in/out widget is an example of how you might combine other components\nto create a new UI element. This package contains color overrides for use inside\na masthead and some custom styles that help it appear according to the design\nsystem requirements simply by using the class `.sign-in-out` and the recommended\nHTML.\n\n",
  "name": "Sign In/Out",
  "usage": "\nUse the sign in/out widget in conjunction with the masthead to display a\ndropdown authenication menu.\n\n#### Markup Example\n```html\n<div class=\"sign-in-out__pos-relative--large\">\n<button aria-controls=\"menu__authentication\" aria-label=\"Sign In\" class=\"button button--icon button--icon-transparent u-pt u-pr--- u-pb u-pl---\" type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"true\">\n  <eds-icon _ngcontent-omu-c1=\"\" filename=\"ico-user-24\" load-method=\"name\"></eds-icon>\n</button>\n <div id=\"menu__authentication\" class=\"sign-in-out u-p0 u-m0\" aria-hidden=\"true | false\" >\n   <div class=\"box--bg-gray-1300 box--border-gray-1100 u-p u-m0\">\n     <form action=\"\" method=\"post\">\n       <fieldset class=\"form__fieldset u-p0 u-m0\">\n           <legend class=\"heading-20 u-mb u-pt----\"><strong>Sign In</strong></legend>\n           <div class=\"u-mb+\">\n             <label class=\"form__label\" for=\"un\">User name</label>\n             <input class=\"textbox\" type=\"text\" id=\"un\" required />\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"u-mb+\">\n             <label class=\"form__label\" for=\"pw\">Password</label>\n             <div class=\"sign-in-out__pos-relative\">\n               <input class=\"textbox u-pr+\" type=\"password\" id=\"pw\" required />\n               <button aria-controls=\"pw\" aria-label=\"Expose password.\" class=\"button button--icon button--icon-transparent sign-in-out__toggle-password\" id=\"toggle-password\" type=\"button\">\n                 <eds-icon\n                   load-method=\"name\"\n                   [svgStyle]=\"svgStyle\"\n                   filename=\"ico-preview-16\">\n                 </eds-icon>\n               </button>\n             </div><!--/.sign-in-out__pos-relative-->\n           </div><!--/.u-mb+-->\n           <div class=\"u-mb+\">\n             <label class=\"checkbox flex u-mb0\" for=\"remember01\">\n                 <input class=\"checkbox__input\" id=\"remember01\" type=\"checkbox\">\n                 <span class=\"checkbox__label\">Remember me</span>\n             </label>\n           </div>\n           <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button flex--center u--1/1\">Sign in</button>\n       </fieldset>\n     </form>\n\n     <div class=\"u-pt u-mb---- text-14 text-align--center\">\n         <a href=\"#!\" class=\"\">Forgot password?</a>\n         <div class=\"u-pb---- u-pt\"><hr /></div>\n         Don't have an account? <a href=\"#!\" class=\"u-ml----\">Register</a>\n     </div>\n   </div>\n </div><!--/.sign-in-out-->\n </div>\n```\n",
